    dc:title "Parasironidae fam. nov., a Cimmerian lineage of Mediterranean Cyphophthalmi (Opiliones), with the description of three new genera and four new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656521>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656525>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656527>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656529>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656533>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656535> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656521>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. A–C. Cimmerosiro krivolutsky gen. et sp. nov. (CIK).A. Male leg I, astragalus (arrow). B. Female leg III, claw.C. Female leg IV, claw. —D–E. C. rhodiensis gen. et sp. nov. (CIK).D. Male leg III, claw.E. Female leg IV, claw. —F. Ebrosiro coiffaiti (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov. (CIK), male III leg, claw." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656521/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656525>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. A–E. Prosessus sensitif on telotarsus of leg I. A–B. Ebrosiro coiffaiti (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov., male (CIK). C. E. coifaitii, female (CIK). D. Cimmerosiro krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov., female (CIK). E. C. krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov., male (CIK). F. C. rhodiensis gen. et sp. nov., female, genital orifice (CIK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656525/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656527>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Ebrosiro coifaitii (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov., female (CIK), ovipositor apical lobes. A. Ventral view. B. Dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656527/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656529>
    dc:description "Fig. 4.Sensilla on pedipalp coxae. A–B. Cimmerosiro krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov. (CIK) (A, lateral view; B, dorsal view). C–D. Ebrosiro coiffaiti (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov. (CIK). E–F. Meghalaya sp. (Stylocellidae) (CIK). Ch = chelicerae; PCx = pedipalp coxae; Tr = pedipalp trochanter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656533>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Pedipalp coxae with bristle-like “sensilla” in Sironidae. A–B. Siro rubens Latreille, 1804 (CIK). C–D. Cyphophthalmus serbicus (Hadži, 1973) (CIK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656533/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656535>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Pedipalp coxae. A–C. Sironidae. D. Parasironidae fam. nov. A. Cyphophthalmus duricorius Joseph, 1868 (CIK). B. Siro rubens Latreille, 1804 (CIK). C. Neosiro exilis (Hoffman, 1963) (CIK). D. Ebrosiro coiffaiti (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov. (CIK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656535/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

